data.description: Bring your golf clubs to this 3 bed/2 bath rancher in the Prairie Falls subdivision just a short golf cart drive to the Prairie Falls Golf Course Club House. This just under 1,300 sf home has a great layout with the split bedroom design and an open concept living area.  Vaulted ceilings and large windows make the space feel bright and airy.  The backyard has a concrete patio ready for entertaining and mature trees provide excellent shade.  RV parking is also available on the side of the house along with a backyard shed for extra storage. This home is in close proximity to not only Prairie Falls Golf Course, but also the Post Falls City Beach and downtown area.  This home is a Hole-in-One!
